name: Save the Hot Potato!
description: Sale of this NFT will be used to bail out the #HENhotpotato (OBJKT#181700) from its capitalist jail. The 1/1 "Hot Potato." NFT was supposed to be sent directly to friends' wallets; no swaps/sales necessary. We wanted to create a running list of wallets that held AND passed the tater. At the time of this writing, it's swapped to the marketplace. Funds from this sale this NFT — POTATO BAIL — will go to buy back the Hot Potato so that we can pass it freely to the next person via airdrop to keep the game going indefinitely. Mucho thankso!
